Lab Five Dining Philosophers:

A program that shows a solution to the Dining Philosophers
problem. The program output shows the progress of the code and indicate
who is holding or releasing forks and who is eating and thinking

Author:
Name: Marcel Zama
College Id: C00260146
Date 24/10/2023

